The paper proposes a CNN-based technique for precise localization of pathology, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The technique involves multi-level learning in CNNs, which can also be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also applies the technique to medical imaging data, which can be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM).
